##################################################
#  Satellite Server 5.7 automation Installation  #
##################################################

This guide is how to use this tool to do Satellite Server5.7 automation installation.

1. Update parameters from Properties.py file

Update satellite installation ISO file
#satellite_ISO = '/root/Satellite_Software/satellite-5.7.0-20150108-rhel-6-x86_64.iso'

Update Satellite activate cert file for RHN
#satellite_cert = "/home/Satellite_Software/satellite5.7_cert.crt"

Update Satellite activate cert file for RHN QA
#QA_satellite_cert = "/home/Satellite_Software/sat57QARHN-test-resigned.cert"

Update answer file path ,there is a answers.txt under directory "entitlement-tests/Tools/SAT5_Setup/"
#answerfile_path = "/root/entitlement-tests/Tools/SAT5_Setup/"

2. Update "entitlement-tests/Tools/SAT5_Setup/answers.txt"

#admin-email = yanpliu@redhat.com
#rhn-username = qa@redhat.com
#rhn-password = 5ZZaEeysLP5Fb9PM
#ssl-set-city = Beijing
#ssl-set-state = Haidian
#ssl-set-country = CN
#ssl-set-org = EntitlementQE
#ssl-password = redhat
#satellite-cert-file = /root/Satellite_Software/satellite5.7_cert.crt

3. If the RHN & RHN QA account information change, you should update these information both in
Properties.py and answers.txt

Properties.py
#[RHN information]
account_rhn = {
    "Live": {
        "username": "qa@redhat.com",
        "password": "5ZZaEeysLP5Fb9PM"
    },
    "QA": {
        "username": "qa@redhat.com",
        "password": "redhatqa"
    }
}
server_url = {
    "QA": "https://xmlrpc.rhn.qa.redhat.com/XMLRPC",
    "Live": "https://xmlrpc.rhn.redhat.com/XMLRPC"
}

answers.txt
rhn-username = qa@redhat.com
rhn-password = 5ZZaEeysLP5Fb9PM



4. Run the tool

1) Install Satellite 5.7 Server for RHN Live
# python SatelliteSetup.py -r Live  or  #python SatelliteSetup.py --rhn=Live
2) Install Satellite 5.7 Server for RHN QA
# python SatelliteSetup.py -r QA  or  #python SatelliteSetup.py --rhn=QA


